Eindtijd & Profetie";"Cpl. Zoharya
column3: Liaison to Platoon Commander in the Search and Rescue Brigade shares:

column1: Last night there were sirens and rockets falling everywhere. We were told to put on our gear and be ready in five minutes. We left our bomb shelters and went as fast as we could to a building that was hit in Petah Tikva.
The cars there were exploded and melting. We entered a half-collapsed building and saw tons of broken and shattered glass.
Our mission on the ground is to help as many civilians as possible. We went to every single door
column2: to see that everyone managed to get out
column3: and that if they needed help or medical assistance they got it.

column1: I drafted five months ago. I’m 19 years old; I’m actually still in training. These past few days we’ve been on-call 24/7. You go to eat
column2: and you eat in 10 minutes because you have no idea what’s going to happen.

column1: I think people just don’t understand the situation we’re living in here. However
column2: we are helping people and giving them a sense of safety
column3: and that makes everything worth it"""

column3: text = ""Israel reports ‘likely’ link between Pfizer & HEART PROBLEMS \n\n"")
column4: ""The second dose of the Pfizer Covid-19 vaccine has a 'probable link' to MYOCARDITIS in young men (an inflammation of the heart muscle). That's according to Israel's Health Ministry.\n\n275 cases of myocarditis have been reported across the country in men under 30
column5: from December 2020 until May 2021.  Of which
column6:
148 of them occurred SHORTLY after their jab.

The link was found to be stronger in people aged 16-19 compared to other groups. Although Pfizer was not mentioned by name in the report it has been almost exclusively used in Israel.

The pharma giant told Reuters that it was aware of the Israeli report but has not established a causal link to its vaccine.

The speed with which Yusen Zhou filed the vaccine patent - and his mysterious death less than three months later - have added fuel to theory that China knew about the virus earlier than admitted.
